#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.count_nonzero.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.count\\_nonzero"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.count_nonzero.count_nonzero:1 of
msgid "Counts the number of non-zero values in the tensor ``a``."
msgstr "计算张量 ``a`` 中非零值的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.count_nonzero.count_nonzero:3 of
msgid ""
"The word \"non-zero\" is in reference to the Python 2.x built-in method "
"``__nonzero__()`` (renamed ``__bool__()`` in Python 3.x) of Python "
"objects that tests an object's \"truthfulness\". For example, any number "
"is considered truthful if it is nonzero, whereas any string is considered"
" truthful if it is not the empty string. Thus, this function "
"(recursively) counts how many elements in ``a`` (and in sub-tensors "
"thereof) have their ``__nonzero__()`` or ``__bool__()`` method evaluated "
"to ``True``."
msgstr ""
"“非零”一词参考了 Python 2.x 的内置方法 ``__nonzero__()``（在 Python 3.x"
" 中重命名为 ``__bool__()``），用于测试对象的“真实性”。例如，任何非零"
"数字被认为是真实的，而任何非空字符串也被认为是真实的。因此，此函数（递归"
"地）计算 ``a``（及其子张量）中 ``__nonzero__()`` 或 ``__bool__()`` 方法"
"返回 ``True`` 的元素数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.count_nonzero.count_nonzero of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.count_nonzero.count_nonzero:13 of
msgid "The tensor for which to count non-zeros."
msgstr "需要计算非零值数量的张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.count_nonzero.count_nonzero:15 of
msgid ""
"Axis or tuple of axes along which to count non-zeros. Default is None, "
"meaning that non-zeros will be counted along a flattened version of "
"``a``."
msgstr ""
"计算非零值的轴或轴的元组。默认为 None，表示将沿 ``a`` 的展平版本计算"
"非零值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.count_nonzero.count_nonzero of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.count_nonzero.count_nonzero:20 of
msgid ""
"**count** -- Number of non-zero values in the array along a given axis. "
"Otherwise, the total number of non-zero values in the tensor is returned."
msgstr "**count** -- 给定轴上数组中非零值的数量。否则，返回张量中非零值的总数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.count_nonzero.count_nonzero of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.count_nonzero.count_nonzero:27 of
msgid ":py:obj:`nonzero`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.count_nonzero.count_nonzero:28 of
msgid "Return the coordinates of all the non-zero values."
msgstr "返回所有非零值的坐标。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.count_nonzero.count_nonzero:31 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

